#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:0.2"
msgid "9. Gaṅgāpeyyālavagga "
msgstr "9. Abbreviated Texts on the Ganges "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 77–88. Gaṅgānadīādisutta → gaṅgādisuttāni (bj)
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:0.3"
msgid "77–88. Gaṅgānadīādisutta "
msgstr "77–88. The Ganges River, Etc. "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gaṅgā nadī pācīnaninnā pācīnapoṇā pācīnapabbhārā; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the Ganges river slants, slopes, and inclines to the east. "

msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satta bojjhaṅge bhāvento satta bojjhaṅge bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro. "
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant who develops and cultivates the seven awakening factors slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.3"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satta bojjhaṅge bhāvento satta bojjhaṅge bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro? "
msgstr "And how does a mendicant who develops the seven awakening factors slant, slope, and incline to extinguishment? "

msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go. "

msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.5"
msgid "evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satta bojjhaṅge bhāvento satta bojjhaṅge bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant who develops and cultivates the seven awakening factors slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.6"
msgid "(Yāva esanā pāḷi vitthāretabbā.) "
msgstr "(To be expanded for each of the different rivers as in SN 45.91–102.) "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.7"
msgid "Gaṅgāpeyyālavaggo navamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.135, sc2
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:2.1"
msgid "Cha pācīnato ninnā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:2.2"
msgid "cha ninnā ca samuddato; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:2.3"
msgid "Dvete cha dvādasa honti, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:2.4"
msgid "vaggo tena pavuccatīti. "
msgstr ""

